name: User tries to view the free liter history screen details
description: User tries to view free liter transactions
descriptionHtml: User tries to view free liter transactions

testStage.description: User tries to view free liter transactions

steps.name: I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I get the text "FREE LITERS HISTORY" from the Account Screen
I check that the application text: "FREE LITERS HISTORY" is equals to expected value: "FREE LITERS HISTORY"
I click on "FREE LITERS HISTORY" tab
I click on month from month picker list for month having transactions
I check expiration label on Free liters screen
I check that the application text: "500,00 L will expire on 31.08.2026" isn't empty
I click on month from month picker list for month having free liters history
I scroll months to left
I scroll months to left
I scroll months to left
I scroll months to left
I validate Free liters history no Of Free Liters Burnt or Earned Negative
I check that "No free liters this month" from Free Liter history screen is displayed
I check that the application text: "+500,00 L" isn't empty
I validate Free liters history Available Text
I check that the application text: "Free Liters" isn't empty
I validate Free liters history Date
I check that the application text: "Sep 11, 2024 2:28 PM" isn't empty
I validate footer text on Free liters screen
I check that the application text: "Score 1 liter for every 50 you pump, plus game rewards for even more savings (Danish customer only)." isn't empty

parameters.name: actual
parameters.value: Score 1 liter for every 50 you pump, plus game rewards for even more savings (Danish customer only).
